name: Mackenzie Canadian Ultra Short Bond Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive Canadian Ultra-Short Bond Index, or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in Canadian corporate and government liquid short debt instruments. The Fund seeks to provide longterm capital appreciation.
